                <p class="intro text-white"><strong>hsbc.com</strong> provides a portal, or gateway, to the financial services offered by members of the <strong>HSBC Group</strong>. The Site is owned by <strong>HSBC Holdings plc</strong>.</p>
<p class="para text-white">HSBC Holdings plc is a public limited company registered in England and Wales under Company Register Number 617987 and with its registered office at 8, Canada Square, London, England E14 5HQ.</p>
                
            </article>
