                <p class="para-intro">Before using this Site, you should read these Terms carefully, as well as our&nbsp;<a href="/terms-and-conditions/privacy-policy" title="Privacy Policy">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="/cookie-policy" title="Cookie Policy">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>
<p class="para-intro">The information contained on the Site is for information purposes only. HSBC Holdings plc does not hold itself out as providing legal, financial or other advice via the Site.</p>
